author: ArcOnyx
description: Get the data for the latest earthquake at or above a specified MMMI in the New Zealand region from GeoNet.
install_msg: Thanks for installing Quake! A couple of things worth noting. Firstly, this cog gets its data from the wonderful https://www.geonet.org.nz and so is only useful for New Zealand. Secondly, quakes may take a short time to appear on the site and so you'll want to wait a minute or two after a quake to run the command.
name: Quake
short: Get latest earthquake info from GeoNet
